{"type":"message","id":"6eb287e0","parentId":"e0adbab7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:23:56.556Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, March 18th, 2026 — 12:23 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-17 16:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773764636554}}
