{"type":"message","id":"21e418fe","parentId":"aeda13ac","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:24:27.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering current skills**\n\nI need to provide an answer about current skills, possibly by listing them based on prior work or preferences. It's likely necessary to use memory search before diving into specifics, though I might not need it here. The user asked for “current skills,” which I can interpret directly. I should include a concise list of available skills that I can trigger based on the user’s preferences. I'll keep it simple and straightforward!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 目前我这边挂着这些技能，常用的都能直接上：\n\n- 飞书文档：feishu-doc / feishu-create-doc / feishu-fetch-doc / feishu-update-doc  \n- 飞书云盘与权限：feishu-drive / feishu-perm  \n- 飞书知识库：feishu-wiki  \n- 飞书多维表格：feishu-bitable  \n- 飞书日历：feishu-calendar  \n- 飞书消息读取：feishu-im-read  \n- 飞书任务：feishu-task  \n- 飞书排障：feishu-troubleshoot  \n- 飞书频道规则：feishu-channel-rules（当前会话默认生效）\n\n还有一些通用技能：\n\n- weather：查天气  \n- web-search-pro：精细化联网搜索  \n- clawhub：安装/更新技能  \n- mcporter：调 MCP 服务  \n- healthcheck：安全检查/主机巡检  \n- node-connect：设备配对与连接排障  \n- skill-creator：创建/整理技能  \n- skill-vetter：技能安全审查  \n- humanizer-zh：把文字改得更像人写的\n\n你要是愿意，我也可以顺手给你分两类：\n1. **我现在最擅长的**\n2. **你目前最可能用得上的**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":416,"output":448,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773764658566}}
