{"type":"message","id":"78195495","parentId":"9142a992","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:29:59.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating skills resources**\n\nI think the user is asking about current skills related to ClawHub instead of SkillHub. This might suggest that memory isn't necessary for this question. Since there’s no clear connection to specific skills, I consider whether ClawHub could be relevant. I should look closely at the SKILL.md file from ClawHub to find the most specific skill that applies to what the user needs. Let's dig into that file and clarify!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aRMHZrmvahD7vz5B9daeESIT","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zbb/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":725,"output":179,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773764987996}}
{"type":"message","id":"80b0dc92","parentId":"78195495","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:29:59.241Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_aRMHZrmvahD7vz5B9daeESIT","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773764999237}}
{"type":"message","id":"ece08950","parentId":"80b0dc92","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:30:05.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有，叫 **ClawHub**，不是 SkillHub。  \n它是拿来**搜索、安装、更新、发布技能**的；你要的话我现在可以帮你看本地已经装了哪些，或者直接去搜新技能。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":575,"output":62,"cacheRead":33920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773764999241}}
