{"type":"message","id":"cd5faba2","parentId":"6fbee9a7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:31:42.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying available tools**\n\nIt seems like the user wants to know about two things: LanceDB and web search. I should mention that LanceDB isn't currently listed as a first-class skill, but web search is available. I think it's best to keep the response concise and directly address their asks. There’s no need to use memory unless I need to reference any prior preferences. It sounds like no additional tools are needed for this query!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] **网页搜索**有，当前可用两路：\n\n- **web_search**：直接联网搜，适合快速找信息\n- **web-search-pro**：更细，适合限定站点、时间范围、新闻、深搜这类需求\n\n你刚提的 **LanceDB**，**目前不在我现成挂载的技能/插件列表里**。  \n如果你想装相关能力，我可以先按你之前定的规矩，**先用 `skill-vetter` 做安全审查**，再去 ClawHub 看有没有合适的技能。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1522,"output":283,"cacheRead":34304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36109,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765086353}}
