{"type":"message","id":"16bd48cf","parentId":"78d423e7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:33:26.185Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering web search issues**\n\nI want to provide a brief answer. It seems the web search failed due to a leaked key, which isn’t ideal. I might suggest using a web-search-pro option if it's configured or perhaps updating the key. Those could be potential solutions! There's really no need to worry about memory in this case. I just want to help the user get past this obstacle and find a workaround!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，**挂的是当前 `web_search` 背后的 Gemini API key**。报错很直接：**这个 key 被判定为泄露，已经被拒用了**。  \n\n现在有两条路：\n\n- **换一个新的 Gemini key**，把搜索恢复\n- **改走别的搜索源**，比如你这边如果配了 `web-search-pro` 的 Tavily / Exa / Serper / SerpAPI，也能顶上\n\n你要的话，我可以继续帮你：\n1. **查现在系统里还剩哪些可用搜索源**\n2. **指导你把这个坏掉的 key 换掉**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3490,"output":213,"cacheRead":35328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765197995}}
