{"type":"message","id":"b5f8d2ce","parentId":"9504ee51","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:36:11.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring alternatives for web search**\n\nI need to provide alternatives since the user’s asking about their current settings rather than previous preferences. It seems the built-in web search might be broken due to a leaked key. Perhaps I could suggest using the web-search-pro skill that requires API keys or doing manual browsing. I might want to mention the option of fetching known URLs, but I'll need to check with the user before modifying any configurations.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有，至少还有三条路：\n\n1. **`web-search-pro`**  \n   这是现成备选，能走 **Tavily / Exa / Serper / SerpAPI**，比内置搜索还细。  \n   前提是环境里得有可用的 API key；如果现在没配，那也跑不起来。\n\n2. **浏览器直搜**  \n   我可以直接开浏览器去搜 Google / Bing / GitHub / 官网，手动帮你找。  \n   这个不依赖刚才那个挂掉的搜索 key，适合现在立刻救火。\n\n3. **已知站点直抓**  \n   如果你给我关键词或目标站点，我可以用 `web_fetch` 直接抓官网、文档、GitHub 页面内容。  \n   这不算“全网搜索”，但查单个项目很够用。\n\n如果你想彻底修好“网页搜索”这件事，最稳的是两种：\n- **换掉当前坏掉的内置搜索 API key**\n- **给 `web-search-pro` 配一套新的 key**（推荐 Tavily 起步）\n\n你要我现在先走哪条？  \n**A. 直接用浏览器帮你搜 LanceDB**  \n**B. 我帮你检查 `web-search-pro` 现在有没有可用 key**  \n**C. 我帮你定位并修当前坏掉的 web_search 配置**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":885,"output":566,"cacheRead":38400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765356775}}
