h over petabytes of multimodal data and vectors with ease. ## **Demo: Multimodal Search by Keyword, Vector or with SQL**. * **Fast Vector Search**: Search billions of vectors in milliseconds with ...\n\n- **LanceDB | Vector Database for RAG, Agents & Hybrid Search** (71%)\n  https://lancedb.com/\n  Why Multimodal Data Needs a Better Lakehouse? From agents to models, from search to training, one platform for all your AI data and workloads. ## AI Needs Better Data Infrastructure. Data lakes only handle tabular data, search engines just work with vectors, and neither work well with multimodal data. LanceDB provides one place for all your AI data and workloads so your team can move fast from ide..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7529,"aggregated":"TAVILY_API_KEY=[set]\nEXA_API_KEY=[set]\n\n---\n## Search: LanceDB\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nLanceDB is an open-source vector database for multimodal AI, supporting scalable vector search and multimodal data management. Founded in 2022, it raised $30 million in Series A funding. It offers fast, production-ready search capabilities.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **The LanceDB Administrator's Handbook: A Comprehensive Tutorial ...** (87%)\n  https://fahadsid1770.medium.com/the-lancedb-administrators-handbook-a-comprehensive-tutorial-on-live-database-manipulation-and-5e6915727898\n  LanceDB is a modern vector database designed to store, search, and query high-dimensional embeddings, especially for applications involving\n\n- **LanceDB - LinkedIn** (87%)\n  https://www.linkedin.com/company/lancedb\n  Overview:\nLanceDB is a developer-friendly, open source database for multimodal AI. From hyper scalable vector search to advanced retrieval for RAG, from streaming training data to interactive exploration of large scale AI datasets, LanceDB is the best foundation for your AI application.\n\nWebsite: https://lancedb.com/\nCrunchbase Url: https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/lancedb?utm_source=linked...\n\n- **LanceDB - GitHub** (76%)\n  https://github.com/lancedb\n  Developer-friendly OSS embedded retrieval library for multimodal AI. Search More; Manage Less. HTML 9.5k 791. Repositories. Loading. Type. Select type.\n\n- **Developer-friendly OSS embedded retrieval library for multimodal AI ...** (74%)\n  https://github.com/lancedb/lancedb\n  **How to Install**  ✦ **Detailed Documentation** ✦ **Tutorials and Recipes** ✦ **Contributors**. LanceDB is designed for fast, scalable, and production-ready vector search. You can store, index, and search over petabytes of multimodal data and vectors with ease. ## **Demo: Multimodal Search by Keyword, Vector or with SQL**. * **Fast Vector Search**: Search billions of vectors in milliseconds with ...\n\n- **LanceDB | Vector Database for RAG, Agents & Hybrid Search** (71%)\n  https://lancedb.com/\n  Why Multimodal Data Needs a Better Lakehouse? From agents to models, from search to training, one platform for all your AI data and workloads. ## AI Needs Better Data Infrastructure. Data lakes only handle tabular data, search engines just work with vectors, and neither work well with multimodal data. LanceDB provides one place for all your AI data and workloads so your team can move fast from ide...","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773765627507}}
{"type":"message","id":"1578e2bf","parentId":"0d472cb9","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:40:37.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以了，`web-search-pro` 这条路是通的，我刚用它搜到了。  \n\n**LanceDB** 简单说就是一个**面向 AI / RAG / 多模态检索的开源向量数据库**，特点是：\n- 主打 **vector search + hybrid search + 多模态数据**\n- 偏 **developer-friendly / embedded**，比较适合做本地或应用内检索层\n- 官网：<https://lancedb.com/>\n- GitHub 组织：<https://github.com/lancedb>\n- 主仓库：<https://github.com/lancedb/lancedb>\n\n这次命中里比较靠谱的源主要是：\n- 官网介绍：LanceDB 把自己定位成 **Vector Database for RAG, Agents & Hybrid Search**\n- GitHub：强调 **fast, scalable, production-ready vector search**\n- 另外还搜到 LinkedIn / Medium 这类外围介绍，但一手信息还是官网和 GitHub 最值钱\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续帮你做任一项：\n1. **总结 LanceDB 的能力、适用场景、优缺点**\n2. **拿它和 Chroma / FAISS / Milvus / pgvector 对比**\n3. **继续搜“LanceDB + OpenClaw / MCP / RAG 集成方案”**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":692,"output":302,"cacheRead":40576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765627512}}
