{"type":"message","id":"2da0cd76","parentId":"0e623820","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:41:36.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering search options**\n\nIt seems that the user is asking about \"mem0\" and looking for project-related information. I think I should probably use the web-search-pro tool since it's the most relevant skill for this task. \n\nHowever, if the question is just about current plugins, that doesn't necessarily require a specific search. Still, to be safe, I'll proceed with executing the search for \"mem0\" to make sure I cover the user's request adequately.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6rnJQo5GuOYMPB6Lj7g9vsdy","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-search-pro/scripts/search.mjs \"mem0\" -n 5","workdir":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1089,"output":218,"cacheRead":40448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773765688947}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ecd9fcb","parentId":"2da0cd76","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:41:44.003Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6rnJQo5GuOYMPB6Lj7g9vsdy","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Search: mem0\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nMem0 is a memory layer for AI agents, backed by Y Combinator and raising $24M. It enhances AI applications with scalable, self-improving memory, reducing costs and improving accuracy. Mem0 compresses chat history to optimize memory, minimizing latency and token usage.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **mem0 (@mem0ai) / Posts / X** (91%)\n  https://x.com/mem0ai\n  Mem0 is the memory layer for AI agents. YC-backed, $24M raised, 45k+ GitHub stars, used by developers at some of the largest companies globally. We're past “\n\n- **Mem0 - The Memory Layer for your AI Apps** (90%)\n  https://mem0.ai/\n  Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised AI experiences that cut costs and enhance user delight. Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised AI experiences that cut costs and enhance user delight. Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised ...\n\n- **AI Memory Research: 26% Accuracy Boost for LLMs** (87%)\n  https://mem0.ai/research\n  ## Mem0: Building Production- Ready AI Agents with Scalable Long-Term Memory. **A scalable memory-centric algorithm that dynamically extracts and retrieves key conversational facts—delivering 26 % relative accuracy gains over OpenAI on the LOCOMO benchmark, with 91 % lower p95 latency and 90 % fewer tokens.**. Mem0ᵍ enhances Mem0 by storing memories as a directed, labeled graph. On the LOCOMO benc...\n\n- **Mem0: The Memory layer for your AI apps** (82%)\n  https://www.ycombinator.com/companies/mem0\n  [![Image 1: Y Combinator](blob:http://localhost/c6d4ffc5fac88acf28c784304b6511e4)](https://www.ycombinator.com/ \"Y Combinator\")Open menu. [About](https://www.ycombinator.com/about). [Companies](https://www.ycombinator.com/companies). [Library](https://www.ycombinator.com/library). [![Image 2: Y Combinator](blob:http://localhost/c6d4ffc5fac88acf28c784304b6511e4)](https://www.ycombinator.com/ \"Y Com...\n\n- **Mem0: Long-Term Memory and Personalization for Agents** (81%)\n  https://microsoft.github.io/autogen/0.2/docs/ecosystem/mem0/\n  # Mem0: Long-Term Memory and Personalization for Agents. Mem0 Platform provides a smart, self-improving memory layer for Large Language Models (LLMs), enabling developers to create personalized AI experiences that evolve with each user interaction. At a high level, Mem0 Platform offers comprehensive memory management, self-improving memory capabilities, cross-platform consistency, and centralized ..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7465,"aggregated":"## Search: mem0\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nMem0 is a memory layer for AI agents, backed by Y Combinator and raising $24M. It enhances AI applications with scalable, self-improving memory, reducing costs and improving accuracy. Mem0 compresses chat history to optimize memory, minimizing latency and token usage.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **mem0 (@mem0ai) / Posts / X** (91%)\n  https://x.com/mem0ai\n  Mem0 is the memory layer for AI agents. YC-backed, $24M raised, 45k+ GitHub stars, used by developers at some of the largest companies globally. We're past “\n\n- **Mem0 - The Memory Layer for your AI Apps** (90%)\n  https://mem0.ai/\n  Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised AI experiences that cut costs and enhance user delight. Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised AI experiences that cut costs and enhance user delight. Mem0 is a universal, self‑improving AI memory layer for LLM applications, powering personalised ...\n\n- **AI Memory Research: 26% Accuracy Boost for LLMs** (87%)\n  https://mem0.ai/research\n  ## Mem0: Building Production- Ready AI Agents with Scalable Long-Term Memory. **A scalable memory-centric algorithm that dynamically extracts and retrieves key conversational facts—delivering 26 % relative accuracy gains over OpenAI on the LOCOMO benchmark, with 91 % lower p95 latency and 90 % fewer tokens.**. Mem0ᵍ enhances Mem0 by storing memories as a directed, labeled graph. On the LOCOMO benc...\n\n- **Mem0: The Memory layer for your AI apps** (82%)\n  https://www.ycombinator.com/companies/mem0\n  [![Image 1: Y Combinator](blob:http://localhost/c6d4ffc5fac88acf28c784304b6511e4)](https://www.ycombinator.com/ \"Y Combinator\")Open menu. [About](https://www.ycombinator.com/about). [Companies](https://www.ycombinator.com/companies). [Library](https://www.ycombinator.com/library). [![Image 2: Y Combinator](blob:http://localhost/c6d4ffc5fac88acf28c784304b6511e4)](https://www.ycombinator.com/ \"Y Com...\n\n- **Mem0: Long-Term Memory and Personalization for Agents** (81%)\n  https://microsoft.github.io/autogen/0.2/docs/ecosystem/mem0/\n  # Mem0: Long-Term Memory and Personalization for Agents. Mem0 Platform provides a smart, self-improving memory layer for Large Language Models (LLMs), enabling developers to create personalized AI experiences that evolve with each user interaction. At a high level, Mem0 Platform offers comprehensive memory management, self-improving memory capabilities, cross-platform consistency, and centralized ...","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773765703999}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4f72cfa","parentId":"9ecd9fcb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:41:57.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有，刚替你搜了。**mem0** 基本可以理解成给 AI / Agent 用的**记忆层**：\n\n- 官网：<https://mem0.ai/>\n- 定位：给 LLM 应用做**长期记忆、用户画像、会话压缩、记忆提取与检索**\n- 常见卖点：**减少 token 消耗、提升个性化、跨会话保留信息**\n- 相关材料里提到它是 **YC 背景**，而且在推“self-improving memory”这套叙事\n\n搜到的主结果大概是这些：\n- mem0 官网\n- mem0 research 页面\n- YC 公司页\n- X / 社媒主页\n- Microsoft AutoGen 生态里的 mem0 集成说明\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接给你来一版更有用的：\n1. **mem0 是什么 + 怎么工作**\n2. **mem0 vs LanceDB**\n3. **mem0 适不适合拿来接 OpenClaw / Agent 记忆**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":929,"output":242,"cacheRead":41344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765704005}}
{"type":"message","id":"d73e79ab","parentId":"a4f72cfa","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:43:37.874Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ac055c5ca0c356abc35993ab7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 00:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54ac055c5ca0c356abc35993ab7]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: 2 对比下"}],"timestamp":1773765817870}}
{"type":"message","id":"076d26dd","parentId":"d73e79ab","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:43:58.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Comparing mem0 and LanceDB**\n\nI need to provide an answer comparing mem0 and LanceDB. Since this is a follow-up to prior work, I’m thinking there could be no need to rely on memory for this. It sounds like the user is asking for a direct comparison, so I'll maybe mention the search results I found. Using a web search could give me enough information, and I can compare them succinctly to keep it clear and straightforward.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 行，那就把 **mem0 和 LanceDB** 摆一起说。\n\n**一句话先说结论：**\n- **mem0** 更像是给 AI Agent 用的**“记忆层 / 记忆系统”**\n- **LanceDB** 更像是通用的**“向量数据库 / 检索底座”**\n\n不是一类东西，虽然都能碰到“检索”和“记忆”。\n\n**直观区别：**\n\n- **mem0**\n  - 重点在：帮 Agent **记住用户、对话、偏好、长期信息**\n  - 更偏应用层：抽取记忆、压缩历史、按语义召回\n  - 目标是：让助手“越聊越懂你”，而不是每次都只靠上下文窗口\n  - 适合：聊天助手、个性化 Agent、长期用户画像、会话记忆\n\n- **LanceDB**\n  - 重点在：存 embedding、建索引、做向量/混合检索\n  - 更偏基础设施层：数据库、索引、查询\n  - 目标是：让系统能高效检索文档、图片、文本块、多模态数据\n  - 适合：RAG、知识库检索、相似搜索、文档问答、多模态搜索\n\n**如果打个比方：**\n- **mem0** 像“会整理记忆的脑子”\n- **LanceDB** 像“存知识和向量的仓库 + 检索引擎”\n\n**你什么时候选哪个：**\n\n- 选 **mem0**，如果你要的是：\n  - 记住“这个用户是谁、喜欢什么、之前说过什么”\n  - 跨会话延续人格和偏好\n  - Agent 的长期记忆，而不是单纯文档检索\n\n- 选 **LanceDB**，如果你要的是：\n  - 把文档切块做 embedding\n  - 检索知识库内容\n  - 做 RAG / semantic search / hybrid search\n  - 管理大量向量或多模态数据\n\n**两者也可以一起用：**\n- **mem0** 管“人和对话的长期记忆”\n- **LanceDB** 管“文档和知识的检索库”\n\n这套组合其实挺合理：\n- Agent 想起“你是谁、你偏好什么” → **mem0**\n- Agent 去查“资料库里有什么” → **LanceDB**\n\n**粗看优劣：**\n\n- **mem0 优点**\n  - 更贴近 Agent 场景\n  - 省你自己做记忆抽取/更新逻辑\n  - 个性化和长期记忆体验更直接\n\n- **mem0 缺点**\n  - 它不是通用数据库底座\n  - 如果你只是做 RAG，可能显得偏“上层”\n\n- **LanceDB 优点**\n  - 检索底座清晰，适合 RAG\n  - 面向向量、多模态、混合搜索更自然\n  - 对“知识库工程”更友好\n\n- **LanceDB 缺点**\n  - 它不会天然替你做好“用户记忆管理”\n  - 你得自己设计记忆抽取、更新、遗忘、优先级这些逻辑\n\n**最简单的选型建议：**\n- 你要做**会记人、会持续聊天的 Agent** → 先看 **mem0**\n- 你要做**知识库问答 / 文档检索 / RAG** → 先看 **LanceDB**\n- 你两个都要 → **mem0 + LanceDB** 分层组合\n\n如果你愿意，我可以继续往下补一版：  \n**“mem0 vs LanceDB vs pgvector vs Chroma” 的更实战选型表。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1368,"output":961,"cacheRead":41472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773765817872}}
